definitions.definition: To mash or push down or in; compress
examples: His favorite part of making preserves with his mother was when he got to smush the raw fruit with the pestle.
That pulled pork meat was smushed in BBQ sauce.

definitions.definition: To engage in intimate contact, especially sexual relations.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To mash or push down or in; compress
secondary_definitions: ( slang , New York , US ) To engage in intimate contact, especially sexual relations.
